OL,3,CDaniel Khalife guilty of spying for
OL,4,CIran but cleared of carrying out a
OL,5,Cbomb hoax
OL,7,FThe 23-year-old, who escaped from
OL,8,FWandsworth prison in September 2023,
OL,9,Fhas been on trial at Woolwich Crown
OL,10,FCourt
OL,12,FDaniel Khalife has been found guilty
OL,13,Fof spying for Iran but cleared of
OL,14,Fcarrying out a bomb hoax, at Woolwich
OL,15,FCrown Court.
OL,17,FOn Thursday morning the jury convicted
OL,18,FKhalife of breaching the Official
OL,19,FSecrets Act and Terrorism Act, after
OL,20,F23 hours of deliberation.
