OL,7,FHe was acquitted of perpetrating a
OL,8,Fbomb hoax.
OL,10,FKhalife, of Kingston, who was wearing
OL,11,Fa blue shirt and pale trousers, calmly
OL,12,Freplaced his glasses as the verdicts
OL,13,Fwere read out, and did not show any
OL,14,Femotion.
OL,16,FThe 23-year-old hit the headlines
OL,17,Fafter escaping Wandsworth prison, by
OL,18,Ftying himself to a food truck in
OL,19,FSeptember 2023, leading to a three day
OL,20,Fman hunt taking place.
