OL,4,CIran but cleared of carrying out a
OL,5,Cbomb hoax
OL,7,FWhile on the run, Khalife bought
OL,8,Fclothes from Marks & Spencer and a
OL,9,Fcoffee from McDonald's in Richmond and
OL,10,Fwalked beside the River Thames before
OL,11,Fbeing caught by police three days
OL,12,Flater.
OL,14,FAs well as charges for escaping prison
OL,15,F- which he initially denied but later
OL,16,Fadmitted - Khalife has been on trial
OL,17,Fat Woolwich Crown Court on charges
OL,18,Fcontrary to the Official Secrets Act
OL,19,Fand Terrorism Act, and was accused of
OL,20,Fperpetrating a bomb hoax.
