OL,7,FProsecutors had said he wanted a
OL,8,Fcareer working as a double agent to
OL,9,Fhelp British security services, and
OL,10,Fhad covertly gathered "a very large
OL,11,Fbody" of names of serving soldiers,
OL,12,Fincluding those in special forces.
