OL,3,CDaniel Khalife guilty of spying for
OL,4,CIran but cleared of carrying out a
OL,5,Cbomb hoax
OL,7,FKhalife, who was based in Stafford
OL,8,Fwhile serving in the British army, had
OL,9,Ftook a photo of a handwritten list of
OL,10,F15 service personnel, including some
OL,11,Ffrom the Special Air Service and
OL,12,FSpecial Boat Service, having been sent
OL,13,Fan internal spreadsheet of promotions
OL,14,Fin June 2021, his trial at Woolwich
OL,15,FCrown Court heard.
OL,17,FHis actions could have put military
OL,18,Fpersonnel's lives at risk and
OL,19,F"prejudiced" the UK's national
OL,20,Fsecurity, the Crown Prosecution
OL,21,FService (CPS) said.
