OL,7,FBethan David, from the CPS, said: "As
OL,8,Fa serving soldier of the British Army
OL,9,FDaniel Khalife was employed and
OL,10,Fentrusted to uphold and protect the
OL,11,Fnational security of this country.
OL,12,FBut, for purposes of his own, Daniel
OL,13,FKhalife used his employment to
OL,14,Fundermine national security.
