OL,7,F"The prosecution was able to use
OL,8,Fmobile phone evidence, notes written
OL,9,Fby Khalife himself and CCTV footage to
OL,10,Fpiece together and demonstrate that
OL,11,FKhalife had gathered and shared much
OL,12,Fof this classified information,
OL,13,Faccepted hundreds of pounds for his
OL,14,Fefforts and even travelled to Turkey
OL,15,Fas part of his unlawful conduct.
