OL,7,F"It is against the law to collate and
OL,8,Fshare secret and sensitive information
OL,9,Ffor a purpose against the interests of
OL,10,Fthe United Kingdom. Such hostile and
OL,11,Fillegal activities jeopardise the
OL,12,Fnational security of the United
OL,13,FKingdom, and the CPS will always seek
OL,14,Fto prosecute anyone that carries out
OL,15,Fcounter state threats."
